A cop and a superhero hugging!

596
00:55:28,450 --> 00:55:30,693
Kinda creepy, no?

597
00:55:33,956 --> 00:55:37,030
Simon, a bit further left!

598
00:55:37,125 --> 00:55:38,651
Voila.

599
00:55:39,795 --> 00:55:41,913
<i>OK... don't move...</i>

600
00:55:43,423 --> 00:55:46,121
Cut the clowning!

601
00:55:47,928 --> 00:55:50,547
This'll be a proper photo, huh?

602
00:55:50,556 --> 00:55:54,301
Watch out, smile...

603
00:55:54,768 --> 00:55:58,092
YEAAAHHH!

604
00:56:39,855 --> 00:56:43,225
All right,
Cast-off, Super-Zucchini.

605
00:56:48,030 --> 00:56:50,899
<i>Good bye!</i>

606
00:57:04,630 --> 00:57:07,840
Let's have a race. Last one in,

607
00:57:07,841 --> 00:57:10,585
