till the end of his life.

608
00:57:10,593 --> 00:57:11,803
Allez, go!

609
00:57:38,330 --> 00:57:42,155
That, is the day you became my children.

610
00:57:53,428 --> 00:57:55,546
Like it?

611
00:58:18,370 --> 00:58:21,455
- You all right, Camille?
- Yes.

612
00:58:21,456 --> 00:58:24,700
