613
00:58:24,960 --> 00:58:28,034
Sometimes people cry
because they're happy.

614
00:58:29,715 --> 00:58:32,038
Right, Raymond?

615
00:58:32,467 --> 00:58:34,460
Yeah...

616
00:58:45,897 --> 00:58:47,523
<i>Dear Simon,</i>

617
00:58:47,524 --> 00:58:52,100
<i>you said The Home was a place for those
who had no one to love them.</i>

618
00:58:53,905 --> 00:58:57,400
<i>I think you're wrong, because
we haven't forgotten you.</i>

619
00:58:58,660 --> 00:59:01,028
<i>And we haven't forgotten the others.</i>

